,`Text0_1_loc2`='Welcome! Step right up, don\'t be shy. This here is my pride and joy... the Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon! Ain\'t she pretty? You look a little big around the mid section, but I think you\'ll fit. Flying is so much fun, want to learn how?'
